Class PrintServiceLocator

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.map.prt.PrintServiceLocator
public class PrintServiceLocator
extends Object

This class provides a set of static methods for getting print service related information such as default print service, media size names, printable area and printer's x,y margins
